{"title":"Zwift news round up: Pride Month ‘Pride-On!’, Virtual Olympics & TRINITY’s Lost Generation","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/28/zwift-news-june-pride-month-trinity-racing-virtual-olympics/","date":1622230779000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>The team over at Zwift has been busy cooking up all kinds of fabulous updates, inclusive rides, and new worlds for users to explore. Here are the coolest and newest happenings in the Zwift world.</p><p>June is Pride Month, and to help celebrate the LGBTQIA+ community Zwift has again partnered with <a href=\"https://www.athleteally.org/\">Athlete Ally</a> and a series of sponsored events and rides. This marks the third year of the partnership in which Zwift and Athlete Ally advocate for equal access in sport.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135526/Pride-On-Zwift-running-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135526/Pride-On-Zwift-running-.jpeg\" alt=\"Pride-On Zwift running\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135526/Pride-On-Zwift-running-.jpeg 1280w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135526/Pride-On-Zwift-running--297x167.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135526/Pride-On-Zwift-running--800x450.jpeg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135526/Pride-On-Zwift-running--120x68.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135526/Pride-On-Zwift-running--768x432.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.