hechrismosier.com/\">Chris Mosier,</a> Olympian <a href=\"https://www.teamusa.org/usa-cycling/athletes/Lea-Davison\">Lea Davidson</a>, and many others will be along to keep users motivated and celebrate.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03.jpeg\" alt=\"Pride-On_Image_Run_03\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03.jpeg 1280w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-297x167.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-800x450.jpeg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-120x68.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-768x432.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-696x392.jpeg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-1068x601.jpeg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-747x420.jpeg 747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03.jpeg 1280w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-297x167.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-800x450.jpeg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-120x68.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-768x432.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-696x392.jpeg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-1068x601.jpeg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135531/Pride-On_Image_Run_03-747x420.jpeg 747w\"></a></p><p>On Sunday, June 13th, there will rides throughout the day in dedication to TogetheRIDE produced by AIDS/Lifecycle. The events will honor the 1.2 million people in the US living with HIV. The idea behind TogetheRIDE is to motivate users to collectively move 1.2 million miles to raise awareness, and fundraise with a goal of $5 million and underline the fight against AIDS.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135603/Zwift-Pride-running-and-riding-jpeg.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135603/Zwift-Pride-running-and-riding-jpeg.jpeg\" alt=\"Zwift Pride running and riding jpeg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp