35603/Zwift-Pride-running-and-riding-jpeg-120x68.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135603/Zwift-Pride-running-and-riding-jpeg-768x432.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135603/Zwift-Pride-running-and-riding-jpeg-696x392.jpeg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135603/Zwift-Pride-running-and-riding-jpeg-1068x601.jpeg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135603/Zwift-Pride-running-and-riding-jpeg-747x420.jpeg 747w\"></a></p><p>So if you need some motivation to ride a little extra in June — here it is!</p><h2><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-large-leaderboard-2\"></span>Zwift Virtual Olympic Series</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding-.jpeg\" alt=\"Zwift olympic series riding\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding-.jpeg 1280w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--297x167.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--800x450.jpeg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--120x68.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--768x432.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--696x392.jpeg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--1068x601.jpeg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--747x420.jpeg 747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding-.jpeg 1280w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--297x167.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--800x450.jpeg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--120x68.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--768x432.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--696x392.jpeg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--1068x601.jpeg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135556/Zwift-olympic-series-riding--747x420.jpeg 747w\"></a></p><p>Now you can be a part of sporting history and ride alongside Olympians and the Zwift Virtual Cycling Series. The Union Cycliste Internationale (UCI), International Olympic Committee (IOC), and Zwift have reached a monumental agreement. They plan to have a complete series of cycling events for the Olympic Virtual Series, scheduled to run June 1-27 — <a href=\"https://www.zwift.com/olympic-virtual-series\">Register here.</a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series-.jpeg\" alt=\"Riding in the Zwift Olympic series\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series-.jpeg 1280w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--297x167.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--800x450.jpeg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--120x68.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--768x432.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--696x392.jpeg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--1068x601.jpeg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--747x420.jpeg 747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series-.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series-.jpeg 1280w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--297x167.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--800x450.jpeg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--120x68.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--768x432.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--696x392.jpeg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--1068x601.jpeg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135538/Riding-in-the-Zwift-Olympic-series--747x420.jpeg 747w\"></a></p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span>The events will focus on mass participation and look to include something for every manor of cyclists. The rides will offer a social experience, launched alongside special podcasts and group workouts with past tons of past Olympians including Nino Schurter and Sir Chris Hoy.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135520/Off-the-front-Zwift-Olympics-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http