14/THe-Lost-Generation-Zwift--297x209.jpeg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135714/THe-Lost-Generation-Zwift--800x564.jpeg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135714/THe-Lost-Generation-Zwift--120x85.jpeg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135714/THe-Lost-Generation-Zwift--768x541.jpeg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135714/THe-Lost-Generation-Zwift--696x490.jpeg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135714/THe-Lost-Generation-Zwift--1068x753.jpeg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135714/THe-Lost-Generation-Zwift--596x420.jpeg 596w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135714/THe-Lost-Generation-Zwift--100x70.jpeg 100w\"></a></p><p>Are you a Junior or U24 racer, bummed about canceled races, and have been waiting all year to show the world what you got? Now’s your chance. Zwift will play host to the <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TrinityRacingTeam\">TRINITY</a> Racing Lost Generation Series starting June 17th.</p><p>The new race league is designed to help young riders showcase their talents and take them to the next level in their cycling careers.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-leader-1\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135550/Trinity-Racing-team-.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/28135550/Trinity-Racing-team-.jpeg\" alt=\"Trinity Racing team\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/